>>  [7,]  0.0    0
>>  [8,]  0.0    0
>>  [9,]  0.0    0
>> [10,]  0.0    0
>> 
>> So, we can see, that implicitly calling Rcpp::as<>() inside the constructor arma::mat() avoids a copy by Rcpp::as<>() - which is just beautiful!
>> 
>> 
